  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ~ SUMMARY ~ </h2>TEN SHOT is an endless arcade game about basic arithmetic.<br>Dodge and weave through waves of numbers- or punch them together and add to 10.<br><br>While made in English, the game is taught through iconography and the shared language of math.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ~ FEATURES ~ </h2>- Full controller support<br>- Simple inputs<br>- 5 unique numeral systems<br>- Hand-crafted waves<br>- In-game statistics<br>- Global Leaderboard<br>- Signed integers<br>- Obscure healing mechanics<br>- 8-bit overflow<br>- Ruptures in the fabric of spacetime",
